 Endpoint : ‘api/recommendation’ Methods = [GET , POST]
state - required - string - State_name,if the state_name is valid and if its is in our record we will use the accumulated weather of state otherwise we will use the indian weather data
city - required - string - City Name,if the state_name is valid and if its is in our record we will use the accumulated weather of state otherwise we will use the indian weather data
api_key - required - string - you have to pass the api key to access our third party services
n - optional - int/float - The Amount of Nitrogen present in Your soil p - optional - int/float - The Amount of phosphorus present in Your soil K - optional - int/float - The Amount of Potassium present in Your Soil Ph - optional - int/float - The PH value of Your soil
